	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3276" cert="high">Ungnadius</persName>, qui ad vos scribit viri clarissimi, etsi stematum rerum gestarum gloria vir sit magnus, tamen id vobis coram deo polliceri atque affirmare ausim pietate omnia superare sua.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quapropter, quicquid in istum hominem contuleritis, id ipsi deo optimo maximo datum existimatote.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rem accelerate, rogo, et, si fieri potest, vestrum iuditium per hunc nuncium, quem intra quinque dies hic esse omnino oportet (nam ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3276" cert="high">Ungnadium</persName> mittendus est) scribite.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quodsi negotia vestra obstiterint, quantocyus fieri potest, rem perpendatis, rogo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quem mitto, affirmo virum simplicem, bonum; is inserviret homini bono in re familiari fideliter, agnovi suos, vel etiam cauponi non adeo incommodus esset.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid ei hac in re prodesse poteritis, in me recipiam factum vestrum omne.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvete et valete, viri optimi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1214" cert="high">Frisio</persName> multas salutes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> 11. augusti anno 59.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vester deditissimus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1536" cert="high">F. Herold</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viris clarissimis <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henricho Bullingero</persName> ac <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodoro Bibliandro</persName>, dominis et amicis.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
